Things to consider designing large system
    1. Architecture pieces that can be used
    2. How these architecture pieces work with each other
    3. how can we best utilize these pieces , right trade off

Core Building Block of Scalable System:-
    1. Load Balancing
    2. Caching
    3. Sharding or Data Partition
    4. Indexes
    5. Proxies
    6. Queues
    7. Redundancy and Replication
    8. Sql vs NoSQL
    9. CAP theorem
    10. Consistent Hashing
    11. Long-polling vs WebSockets vs Server-Sent Events
